<body onload="init({{deadline}}, {{percentageCompleted}}, {{sdsSold}}, {{askEmail}})">

  <section class="first-section">
    <div id="logo"><a href="/"><img class="logo-img" src="images/seeds-logo.png" alt="Logo"></a></div>

    {{#showProgress}}
    <div id="progressbar"></div>
    {{/showProgress}}

    <div id="clockdiv">
      <h1>{{phase}} ends in</h1>
      <div id="clockdiv-container">
        <div>
          <span class="days"></span>
          <div class="smalltext">Days</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="hours"></span>
          <div class="smalltext">Hours</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="minutes"></span>
          <div class="smalltext">Minutes</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="seconds"></span>
          <div class="smalltext">Seconds</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {{^showProgress}}
    <div id="tokenSold"></div>
    {{/showProgress}}

    <div id="discount"><p>Acquire SEEDS Tokens during the Pre-Sale Stage 1 phase for 25% off the listed price:</p></div>

    <!-- Button trigger modal -->
    <div class="buy-button">
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#modalContactForm">
          JOIN PRE-SALE NOW
      </button>
    </div>

    <div id="ethereum"><img src="images/ethereum.jpeg" alt="Ethereum">
      <p>Accepting Ethers: 1 SEEDS Token = {{price}} Ether</p>
    </div>

    <div class="modal fade" id="modalContactForm" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-dialog cascading-modal" role="document">
          <!--Content-->
          <div class="modal-content">

              <!--Header-->
              <div class="modal-header light-blue darken-3 white-text">
                  <h4 class="title"><i class="fa fa-pencil"></i> Enter your email address</h4>
                  <button type="button" class="close waves-effect waves-light" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                      <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                  </button>
              </div>
              <!--Body-->
              <div class="modal-body mb-0">
                 <form role="form" name="modalForm" action="/contribute" method="POST">
                  <div class="md-form form-sm">
                      <i class="fa fa-envelope prefix"></i>
                      <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="form-control">
                      <label for="email">Your email</label>
                  </div>

                  <div class="text-center mt-1-half">
                      <button class="btn btn-primary mb-2" onclick="return validateForm();">Continue <i class="fa fa-send ml-1"></i></button>
                  </div>
                </form>

              </div>
          </div>
          <!--/.Content-->
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="grey-section">
    <h3>What is Seeds?</h3>
    <p>Seeds provides a decentralized, transparent, distributed platform for submitting and fulfilling monetary needs.  When a user makes a Needs Request through Seeds, our recommendation algorithm displays that need to the people within the ecosystem who will be most likely to want to help fulfill it.  Needs submitted to the Seeds system will be granted through crowdsourced monetary gifts, and a Need Request can be money for virtually anything. So as long as it’s legal and the intention is good, we would love to help you get your needs met. :)
    </p>

    <div id="reference-buttons">
      <a target="_blank" href="SEEDS-white-paper.pdf" class="btn btn-green-1 btn">WHITE PAPER</a>
      <a target="_blank" href="SEEDS-one-pager.pdf" class="btn btn-green-2 btn">ONE-PAGER</a>
    </div>

  </section>

  <section>
    <h3>Seeds Tokens</h3>
    <p>Seeds tokens (SEEDS) allow users to make Needs Requests through the Seeds system.  When another user contributes to fulfilling that need, s/he is automatically entered into a lottery that awards a fixed number of tokens at random.  Winners can then submit the Seeds tokens they have won to make Needs Request of their own.
    </p>

    <div id="timeline"><img src="images/timeline.png" alt="timeline"></div>

    <p>The notional value of SEEDS is set at ~$0.04 per token. The final value will be determined by the sale</p>

    <div id="pie-chart"><img src="images/pie-chart.jpg" alt="pie-chart"></div>

    <div class="pie-chart-legend">
      <h4>Tokens allocation</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>1 Billion SEEDS issued</li>
        <li>33% for sale</li>
        <li>33% retained by Seeds</li>
        <li>33% allocated for partners to incentivise the network</li>
        <li>1% to cover token sale costs and fees</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
